INFO 201 AB Final Project

Introduction

Best Bank Of 2017 is a ShinyApp Interface produced by Zegang Cheng, Nathan Magdalera, Tufang Xu, and Shelley Tsui.

band pic

This Shiny App utilizes the Jambase API in order to create an interactive map. The map displays the locations of an artist/band/concert information based on user input. Users can click on individual map markers to learn more information about the concert venues location.
